    <p>Finding genuinely vegan gummy supplements used to mean reading ingredient lists under a magnifying glass. Gelatin, beeswax, carmine, shellac — animal-derived ingredients hid in formulations across every category. That landscape has shifted dramatically. Pectin-based gummies now dominate new product launches, and major brands have reformulated entire lines to be plant-based. The result: you can build a complete vegan supplement stack entirely in gummy form without sacrificing ingredient quality, dosing accuracy, or taste.</p>

